---
description: When the user adds or changes images in the gallery drop folder, sync and publish automatically.
globs:
  - public/images/drop/**
  - content/**
---

When the user mentions new images, uploading work, or updating the gallery:

1. Run `npm run publish` from `~/Documents/infinite-portfolio` (sync → build → git push).
2. If that fails on git push, report the error and tell them to run `./scripts/first-push.sh` once.
3. Do not ask them to edit JSON or run git manually.

Drop folder (source of truth): `public/images/drop/`
- Loose image file → single gallery piece
- Subfolder with images → carousel collection (2–5 images)
